355
00:42:32,770 --> 00:42:35,530
I don't have time for this nonsense with you.

356
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:39,450
Don't worry. She'll be all right.

357
00:42:39,450 --> 00:42:41,940
She was indeed here?!

358
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:45,850
Was it Gu Jian who took Xiaofeng away?

359
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:51,560
I believe that Gu Jian will make sure Xiaofeng is safe.

360
00:42:53,200 --> 00:42:55,590
You don't understand anything.

361
00:42:59,510 --> 00:43:01,020
I...

362
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:06,000
How could I not understand?

363
00:43:08,010 --> 00:43:10,800
I should have let you drink two jugs.

